Ideas:

+ Purpose is to simulate setting up a manufacturing capital in a decedant space empire.
++ Activities include:
    -Hunting for lost blueprints.
    -Setting up factories.
    -Guiding population growth and education.
    -Managing the fiscal requirements of a interstellar faction.
    -Building interstellar vessels.
    -Building items from lost knowledge.
    -Defend territory from invasion.
    -Compete politically with other faction leaders.
    -When diplomacy fails compete militarilly with other factions.
    -Explore and map the universe.
    -Expand your forge to the stars.
    
